text: Lindsey Ann Fraser (born 1958), is a female former diver who competed for Great Britain and England. ==Diving career== Fraser represented Great Britain at the 1980 Summer Olympics and the 1984 Summer Olympics. She also represented England in the 10 metres platform, at the 1982 Commonwealth Games in Brisbane, Queensland, Australia. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:English female divers Category:Divers at the 1982 Commonwealth Games Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Divers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Divers at the 1984 Summer Olympics
